CHANGES
=======

0.9.0
-----

* Rename nats-python as pynats2

0.6.1
-----

* Add dataclasses into requirements.txt

0.6.0
-----

* Add setup scripts
* Improve scheme handling
* Remove \_recv() from \_connect\_tls()
* Make NATSClient.\_\_init\_\_() simple
* Catch exception on ping at \_stop\_waiter()
* Add virtual host support
* Add NATSNoSubscribeClient class
* Revert "Add auto\_reconnect option to NATSClient"
* Add auto\_reconnect option to NATSClient
* Refactor waiter and pinger
* Add ping thread
* Add worker threads for message handling
* Add \_waiter(): threaded wait()
* Add read/send lock for multi-threading
* Support TLS
* [release] back to development

0.5.0
-----

* [release] uprev
* [fix] fixed passing of subscription queue name to the NATS server (#3)
* [ci] switch to Drone CI
* update badges
* fixup mypy issues
* pin minimal required deps
* fixup black dep installation
* back to development

0.4.0
